<i>This body will die.</i>

13
00:00:55,140 --> 00:00:56,360
<i>What about the man?</i>

14
00:00:57,530 --> 00:00:58,700
<i>I see.</i>

15
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:00,490
<i>So that's what the belt is for.</i>

16
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:07,940
<i>I have no choice but to 
