Sleep is beneficial.

35
00:03:22,660 --> 00:03:23,930
Yeah, yeah.

36
00:03:23,930 --> 00:03:27,140
Your well-being is my well-being.

37
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:34,150
Although it's minimal, you're no longer pure.

38
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:37,150
I wonder what she meant by that.

39
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,420
My physical body

40
00:03:38,420 --> 00:03:42,410
