That may be the reason.

42
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,280
Huh?

43
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:50,950
What I mean is that your brain may 
be undergoing changes, as well.

44
00:03:50,950 --> 00:03:52,890
Tamiya Ryoko realized that,

45
00:03:52,890 --> 00:03:56,040
and detected something "inhuman" about you.

46
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,910
