get to see human intercourse.

227
00:14:10,740 --> 00:14:11,820
Go back to sleep.

228
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,250
Who're you talking to?

229
00:14:15,430 --> 00:14:16,790
You followed me home?

230
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:18,490
I just came to apologize.

231
00:14:19,180 --> 00:14:20,000
Okay.

232
00:14:20,740 --> 00:14:21,920
It's fine, then.

233
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,220
Oh?

234
00:14:24,450 --> 00:14:25,550
So we're all good, then.

235
00:14:27,490 --> 00:14:30,550
At least, you and I are good.

236
00:14:31,570 --> 00:14:32,430
Um...

237
00:14:33,210 --> 00:14:34,110
Okay.

238
00:14:45,690 --> 00:14:47,400
S-Sorry.

239
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:49,320
